### NAME TESTS ###

### T29_P32
// User admin retrieve the users
GET http://localhost:4111/api/v1/admin/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic YWRtaW46YWRtaW4=

### T29_Positive test
// Autorized third user can change their name
PUT http://localhost:4111/api/v1/customer/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic QnJpdHRhOkNDYWEzMyEh

{
  "name": "Britta Smith"
}

### T30_Negative test
// Autorized third user can not change their name without missed space in one world
# test data: "name": "Britta Smith"
PUT http://localhost:4111/api/v1/customer/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic QnJpdHRhOkNDYWEzMyEh

{
  "name": "BrittaSmith"
}

### T30_Negative test
// Autorized third user can not change their name consist of three worlds
# test data: "name": "Britta Smith"
PUT http://localhost:4111/api/v1/customer/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Basic QnJpdHRhOkNDYWEzMyEh

{
  "name": "Britta Smith Jons"
}

### T31_Negative test
// Autorized third user can not use digits in the name
# test data: "name": "Britta Smith"
